Package listeners

Interface ToolbarToggleListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
MainController
public interface ToolbarToggleListener
The listener interface for receiving toolbarToggle events. The class that is interested in processing a toolbarToggle event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addToolbarToggleListener method. When the toolbarToggle event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.
